files.Title: EchoHub.Client.AppOrchestrator
files.Summary: Central orchestrator for the EchoHub TUI client. Owns session state and wires UI events to service calls.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.AsyncRunner
files.Summary: Eliminates repeated Task.Run/try/catch/app.Invoke(ShowError) boilerplate. Runs async work on a background thread and routes exceptions to the UI.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ChatColors
files.Summary: Shared color attributes for chat rendering (timestamps, system messages).

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ChatLine
files.Summary: A single line in the chat, composed of colored segments.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ChatListSource
files.Summary: Custom list data source for chat messages with per-character coloring.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ChatSegment
files.Summary: A colored text segment within a chat line.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ColorHelper
files.Summary: Helper to parse hex colors to Terminal.Gui Attributes.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ConnectDialog
files.Summary: A Terminal.Gui dialog for entering server connection and authentication details. Includes a saved servers selector when saved servers are available.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ConnectDialogResult
files.Summary: Result returned from the connect dialog.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.MainWindow
files.Summary: Main Terminal.Gui window for the EchoHub chat client.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ProfileAction
files.Summary: Action selected by the user in their own profile dialog.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ProfileEditDialog
files.Summary: A Terminal.Gui dialog for editing the user's profile (display name, bio, nickname color).

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ProfileEditResult
files.Summary: Result returned from the profile edit dialog.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.ProfileViewDialog
files.Summary: Dialog for viewing a user's server profile. Shows Edit Profile / Set Status buttons when viewing own profile.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.StatusDialog
files.Summary: A Terminal.Gui dialog for setting the user's status and status message.

files.Title: EchoHub.Client.UI.StatusDialogResult
files.Summary: Result returned from the status dialog.

files.Title: EchoHub.Core.Contracts.IEchoHubClient
files.Summary: Methods the server can invoke on connected clients.

files.Title: EchoHub.Server.Irc.IrcClientConnection
files.Summary: Manages a single IRC client TCP connection.

files.Title: EchoHub.Server.Irc.IrcMessage
files.Summary: Parsed representation of an IRC protocol line. Format: [:prefix] COMMAND [params...] [:trailing]
